Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:03.79,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好了嗎？ - 好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:07.00,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嗨 這是 瑞秋 和 菲比的家   - 並且是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.50,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 請   - 走開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.09,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.34,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個我說過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.63,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道 因為你都分到好的字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:20.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而我呢？"這是" "和" 還有"留言" 我不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:23.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 菲比 別鬧了   - 好 不要 那我們交換{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.56,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我都分到好的字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.73,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 我們交換{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.82,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好   - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:32.94,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嗨   - 大家好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.24,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 這是   - 瑞秋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 和   - 菲比的家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.61,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}請...慢著 你是怎麼弄的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不是普通角色對吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:47.71,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲比 待會再錄好嗎？ 我想在天黑前去慢跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你也一起來嘛   - 真的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.25,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對 一定很好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.38,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去公園跑步 當做室友問第一次聯絡威情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.05,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 我們去跑步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:59.72,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 而且那裏有帥哥   - 那就往他們跑過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.35,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.52,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你等我一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.39,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗨 這是瑞秋和菲比的家 請在嗶聲後留言 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.44,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等 你都講完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:12.27,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 你遇到對手了 瑞秋葛林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.50,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老友記 {\fs16}第六季 第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.98,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我剛看完一本很棒的書   - 嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:59.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到了2030年 有些電腦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:04.70,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}能執行跟人腦一樣多的功能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.04,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以理論上你可以把思想記憶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:10.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下載到這種電腦上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:15.84,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後以機器的形態長生不死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.18,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我剛發現我能睜著眼睛睡覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿   - 嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:31.02,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把箱子釘在地上真是個好主意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:36.53,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我沒把箱子釘在地上   - 所以你可以搬走咯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.03,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我這就搬 羅斯有個很好聽的電腦故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家好 這是吉寧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.62,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是我的新室友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.33,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你好   - 你好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.38,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她要來跟我住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.30,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很高興認識你 吉寧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.80,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}勒誇 吉寧勒誇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.76,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我都不知道 好好聽的姓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.64,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是哪裏人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.97,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}澳洲人2星期前剛到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 來自南半球？ - 嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.85,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個我也不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.69,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你做哪一行？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.78,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我是個舞者   - 你是個舞者？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是個舞者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:26.33,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我要去整理東西了   - 我幫你開門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 喬伊   - 什麼事？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.55,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你叫她搬來之前有先面試嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 當然有   - 嗯哼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你到底問了什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.97,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你什麼時候可以搬來？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:50.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝你把她帶到我們身邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.14,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好個大美人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.60,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也喜歡她？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.81,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你看這堆箱子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.74,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我好想趕快約她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.07,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喬伊 你不能約她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是你的室友 那樣會太複雜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.58,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯 千萬不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.54,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你約了她 我就不能約她了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你之前跟一個唐娜交往 後來分手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.21,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}記得你們在超市巧遇的尷尬嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.84,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想像你住在超市裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.34,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.26,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不是   - 噢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.64,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說得對 那樣很不好 我不能約她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.77,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最好也別跟她調情 住得這麼近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.65,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 可能會出事   - 太難了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:42.57,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}畢竟美女當前 我很難不打情罵俏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:46.74,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我老是在你面前 你也沒怎樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有點難過是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要綁鞋帶 你先跑 我就來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好   - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.76,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託 那哪叫跑步 快點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.38,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}（中央咖啡廳）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.77,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是說真的 她跑步的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.27,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像大嘴蛙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.40,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和生化機器人合體{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.28,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡以前好喜歡他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:28.91,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她睡覺之前都會親他的海報{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.28,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.91,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有他的專輯 《全身綠色的煩惱》嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以菲比的姿勢很怪？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.05,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對 而且她還會想再去跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我躲不掉 我跟她住在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.51,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就實話實說嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:55.06,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說得對 我應該跟她直說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.39,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿   - 嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.52,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲比 摩妮卡把我絆倒 我再也不能跑步了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你為什麼要絆倒她？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.32,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}瑞秋 抱歉害你兩個腳踝受傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.24,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 只有一個   - 等著瞧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.33,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 東西都拿出來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.46,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多謝幫忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.17,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喬伊？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看來他回家了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看 還有一個箱子沒拆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.94,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你被騙了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:46.27,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天哪 我差點被嚇出心臟病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想笑想得好辛苦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很像回事嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.82,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不賴吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:57.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡今天要加班 我要把這裏打掃得一塵不染{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.04,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還有還有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我還要下樓去買花送她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}誰會不想跟我住？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.97,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想跟性威的澳洲舞者住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:14.18,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}情況如何？你能不打情罵俏嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}目前還可以 但是好累{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:20.52,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的調情能量一直累積 無處發洩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.31,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.86,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 客廳比較寬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:41.46,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是 我只是想到 我也該拉拉筋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.50,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你應該...   - 啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 怎麼了？ - 沒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.93,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不要打趣我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.26,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我拉筋拉得全身是汗 哈哈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.76,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我去洗個澡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.52,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.69,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉在浴室晾衣服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.73,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的丁字褲很嬌貴 不能烘乾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 啊   - 嗨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.41,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 沒錯   - 是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.88,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看到你抄了慢跑鞋溜出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.25,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你騙我好自己跑步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.13,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是 我沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是我只是跑跑看...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.80,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.72,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}能不能跑 結果可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.64,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託 我又不是白癡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.93,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等 菲比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.57,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同居真的會讓人越來越像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.28,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩德...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.03,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}呃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.87,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.29,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說呢？我在打掃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.79,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你動她的東西有經過她同意嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.63,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒必要 我會把東西都放回去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.09,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全恢復原狀嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然是完全恢復原狀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.97,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這種態度對你沒有幫助{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.06,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她才不會在乎有沒有恢復原狀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.65,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是剛認識摩妮卡嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.15,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她會認同我的體貼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.61,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}並感到窩心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.36,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其實這樣也蠻好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.66,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等你必須搬回去跟喬伊住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.62,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喬伊的新室友就可以來跟我住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.87,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我懂了 你想嚇我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:51.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錢德 摩妮卡對這種事有怪癖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:56.63,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相信我 我跟她住了16年 她會捉狂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天哪 她會壓在你身上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.55,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她才不會 我證明給你看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.72,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我現在就打給她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.43,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}電話擦好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.56,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嗨   - 摩妮卡 你好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.90,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爛透了 什麼事都得我自己來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.82,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其他人只會搞砸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我今晚可能會殺人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.58,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別這樣 沒那麼糟吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是非常糟 想到快見到你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.62,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我才撐得下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我搞不好會設法早退   - 不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.17,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}餐廳似乎很需要你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你跟羅斯在起嗎？ － 一切都很好 再見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.22,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她會宰了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.43,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}電話放反了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.18,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相框應該擺在上面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.44,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們從大型傢俱復原起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:58.11,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比較簡單 先搬沙發{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我沒問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.37,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}位置好像不對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼意思？沙發剛好跟毯子對齊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:14.46,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以走到這邊 輕鬆的把腳翹在...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.80,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.88,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就把沙發往茶几那邊挪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:23.13,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那沙發的背後 就不會跟毯子邊緣對齊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.47,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就把茶几往沙發{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那邊推{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:33.77,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那茶几就不在座位區正中央了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.36,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那茶几就無法配上桌子...羅斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.61,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我該怎麼辦？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:47.03,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不調情 卻還是吸引著她 就像火吸引著飛蛾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.87,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這裏是怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.84,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡會宰了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.80,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要你們的幫忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得想辦法把這個女人嚇跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們最會把女人嚇跑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.10,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可是結過三次婚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 我親眼見識過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:24.07,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們跟女人交柱得好好的 最後卻總是能搞砸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.70,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們的秘訣是什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.49,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們並不會把女人嚇跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.58,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全沒有這回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.71,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們確實會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.29,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}記不記得大學參加春季舞會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.71,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你走向看對眼的女生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.13,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}卻大談愛爾蘭馬鈴薯饑荒？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.30,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你呢？你當年也沒那麼酷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.89,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他每次說完話都會加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.64,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡也不喜歡 也許我應該改掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.73,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對了 女生不喜歡我聊科學{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不只是女生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.86,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太好了 還有呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.03,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她們不喜歡你糾正她們的文法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.58,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她們不喜歡你解釋 你的笑話哪袒好笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她們不喜歡你一直問她們 喜不喜歡你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:22.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 天哪 幸好我有摩妮卡   - 我再也別想談戀愛了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.97,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.60,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 菲比 可以跟你談談嗎？ - 好啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.18,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:39.48,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲比 我只是想跟你道歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.11,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我處理得很差{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.44,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且我不該騙你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.36,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你應該怎樣？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.82,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我應該跟你說實話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.37,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而實話是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:58.21,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我之所以不想跟你跑步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是因為...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:03.13,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你跑步的姿勢有點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.34,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 所以呢？ - 很尷尬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.55,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別人都當我們是瘋子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.80,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你幹嘛在意？ - 因為他們是人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.85,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不認識也不會再見到的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.31,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但他們依舊是人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.31,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有眼睛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.77,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就不怕跟喘氣小姐跑步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咻 咻 咻 咻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.86,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:33.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}難怪你會覺得 跟我跑步很尷尬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你很放不開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:39.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我哪有放不開...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:44.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我才不會放不開 老兄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.26,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒關係 我不是在批評你 你就是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.09,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就比較自由 我從小就這樣跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為這樣才好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:59.52,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你從來沒有往前衝到 腿好像快斷了嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}例如要跑去玩蕩鞦韆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.98,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或是在躲魔鬼時？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.11,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}鄰居的狗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.91,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這盞燈沒擺錯吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.70,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}管他的 我會把女人嚇跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.37,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不行 你不能進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.13,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}羅斯光著身體{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.88,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 什麼？ - 什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不能說我光著身體 她可以看我光著身體{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.55,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼一定要有人光著身體？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.23,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}羅斯為什麼光著身體？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:47.40,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要給錢德看一個東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.69,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光著身體看？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.91,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.07,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我好像有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.37,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}男人病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟錢德的一樣嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}待會再回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.30,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們搞定了你再回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.43,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}浴室洗手台底下 還有錢德的藥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.10,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 再見   - 再見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.23,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝天謝地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.57,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有什麼病？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.78,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒時間了 我們必須專心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.74,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們得把一切恢復原狀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.03,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相簿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:43.12,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相簿裏有一大堆這裏的照片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們可以拿照片來對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.79,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 太好了 好主意   - 是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.38,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說真的 你有什麼病？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.93,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喬伊 我幫你買了啤酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.68,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是"幫誰"吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.85,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:09.31,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我正想叫彼薩 你要一起吃嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.73,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}披薩 我又不是沒吃過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.36,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有什麼問題嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.66,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就明說了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.50,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你很火辣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.21,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很俊俏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.38,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們兩個顯然很有感覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.84,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我們是室友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們不能走上這條路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.51,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 喬伊...   - 不 我是說真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.06,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想像你住在超市裏 這樣你就懂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.94,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我們該怎麼辦？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.23,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不怎麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.65,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我覺得你人很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.32,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我對你沒興趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.58,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}噢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.66,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:10.50,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你人真的很好 我很高興能當你的室友和朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.63,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是我對你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.01,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒有那種感覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.22,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}噢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.30,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了 哈哈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.93,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為我一直想把你嚇跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:29.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相信我 等我一放電 情況就不同了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.56,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 應該不會   - 絕對會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.65,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.70,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.12,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.09,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咻 咻 咻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.39,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿   - 嗨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.40,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對不起 你說得對 感覺好爽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.61,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對吧？你不會在意別人的目光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.44,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才幾秒鐘你就跑不見了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:21.11,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯 感覺真的好棒 我覺得好自由好優雅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.57,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}噢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.95,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小心那匹 馬...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.20,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以進去了嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯哼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.72,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 為什麼東西都變了？ - 再見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.10,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒有變啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.69,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只不過你一進來 房裏變得更亮了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.48,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小茶几位置不對 沙發怪怪的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.11,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}更別提冰箱上的磁鐵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.16,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你別生氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:11.83,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我整理完東西 想做點讓你高興的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.92,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我就大掃除{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.84,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我把東西亂搬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:22.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}卻忘了該怎麼復原 對不起 對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.59,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒關係{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.35,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錢德 你在怕我嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.18,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要我怕你嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:34.48,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:38.02,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託 你做了這麼棒的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.94,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我真的很開心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.69,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道我對東西的擺設有怪癖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.28,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我萬萬沒想到你會擔心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.16,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.70,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然是真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.87,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你最好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.66,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}過來我抱抱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.96,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等 先做該做的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.75,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 現在...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.67,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}羅斯光著身體時坐過哪裏？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.85,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}書上說到了2030年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:13.27,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有些電腦 能執行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.56,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟人腦一樣多的功能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:19.23,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以理論上人可以把思想記憶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.61,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下載到這種電腦上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:24.19,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後以機器的形態長生不死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:32.16,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道我們現在在做什麼嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.08,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們在連結{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.29,Pure Chinese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我該走了{\r}
